---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Spill the Tea"
  description="Tips, rumors, and developments from Morristown's restaurant scene. New openings, closures, construction, and things overheard."
>
  <style>
    .spill-wrap {
      max-width: 620px;
      padding: 4rem 0 6rem;
    }
    .spill-header {
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }
    .spill-header .label {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }
    .spill-header h1 {
      font-family: var(--font-display);
      font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 5vw, 3.2rem);
      line-height: 1.05;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .spill-header .spill-sub {
      font-family: var(--font-body);
      font-size: var(--text-base);
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: var(--color-ink-muted);
      max-width: 500px;
    }
    .spill-tip-box {
      background: var(--color-ink);
      color: var(--color-paper);
      padding: 2rem 2.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
      box-shadow: 4px 4px 0 var(--color-rust);
    }
    .spill-tip-box p {
      font-family: var(--font-body);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin: 0 0 1rem;
    }
    .spill-tip-box p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
    .spill-tip-box a {
      color: var(--color-mustard);
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
    .spill-item {
      border-bottom: 2px solid var(--color-paper-dark);
      padding: 2rem 0;
    }
    .spill-item:first-of-type {
      border-top: 2px solid var(--color-ink);
    }
    .spill-date {
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      color: var(--color-ink-muted);
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    .spill-tag {
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-size: 0.65rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      background: var(--color-rust);
      color: var(--color-paper);
      padding: 0.15rem 0.5rem;
      display: inline-block;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }
    .spill-item h3 {
      font-family: var(--font-display);
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      line-height: 1.2;
      margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
    }
    .spill-item p {
      font-family: var(--font-body);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      line-height: 1.75;
      color: var(--color-ink-muted);
      margin: 0;
    }
    .spill-empty {
      font-family: var(--font-body);
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.8;
      color: var(--color-ink-muted);
      font-style: italic;
      padding: 3rem 0;
      border-top: 2px solid var(--color-ink);
    }
    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .spill-wrap { padding: 3rem 0 4rem; }
      .spill-tip-box { padding: 1.5rem; }
    }
  </style>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="spill-wrap">

      <div class="spill-header">
        <span class="label">The Gossip Rag</span>
        <h1>Spill the Tea.</h1>
        <p class="spill-sub">
          New openings. Closures. Construction. Liquor license transfers. Things overheard.
          Unverified until stated otherwise.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="spill-tip-box">
        <p>
          Got something? A new restaurant filing permits, a For Lease sign going up,
          a chef switching kitchens, construction that doesn't add up —
          <a href="mailto:tips@morristowneats.com">tips@morristowneats.com</a>.
          Anonymous is fine.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="spill-empty">
        The kettle's on. First dispatches coming soon.
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

</BaseLayout>
